{"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/equatableview\/padding(_:_:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/EquatableView"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Adds an equal padding amount to specific edges of this view.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/EquatableView\/padding(_:_:)"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"nonisolated","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"padding","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"_","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"edges","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Edge","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4EdgeO","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Edge"},{"kind":"text","text":"."},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4EdgeO3SetV","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Edge\/Set","text":"Set"},{"kind":"text","text":" = .all, "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"_"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"length"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CGFloat"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil) -> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","text":"View"},{"kind":"text","text":"\n"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"edges","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The set of edges to pad for this view. The default","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Edge\/Set\/all","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"length","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"An amount, given in points, to pad this view on the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"specified edges. If you set the value to ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", OpenSwiftUI uses","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a platform-specific default amount. The default value of this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"parameter is ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"return-value","level":2,"text":"Return Value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A view that’s padded by the specified amount on the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"specified edges.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this modifier to add a specified amount of padding to one or more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"edges of the view. Indicate the edges to pad by naming either a single","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"value from ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Edge\/Set"},{"text":", or by specifying an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/Swift\/OptionSet"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that contains edge values:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["VStack {","    Text(\"Text padded by 20 points on the bottom and trailing edges.\")","        .padding([.bottom, .trailing], 20)","        .border(.gray)","    Text(\"Unpadded text for comparison.\")","        .border(.yellow)","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The order in which you apply modifiers matters. The example above"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"applies the padding before applying the border to ensure that the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"border encompasses the padded region:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can omit either or both of the parameters. If you omit the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"length"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"OpenSwiftUI uses a default amount of padding. If you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"omit the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"edges"},{"type":"text","text":", OpenSwiftUI applies the padding to all edges. Omit both"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to add a default padding all the way around a view. OpenSwiftUI chooses a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"default amount of padding that’s appropriate for the platform and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the presentation context."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["VStack {","    Text(\"Text with default padding.\")","        .padding()","        .border(.gray)","    Text(\"Unpadded text for comparison.\")","        .border(.yellow)","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The example above looks like this in iOS under typical conditions:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To control the amount of padding independently for each edge, use","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View\/padding(_:)-6pgqq"},{"text":". To pad all outside edges of a view by a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"specified amount, use ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View\/padding(_:)-68shk"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"metadata":{"platforms":[{"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"name":"iOS","introducedAt":"13.0","deprecated":false},{"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"name":"macOS","introducedAt":"10.15","deprecated":false},{"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"name":"tvOS","introducedAt":"13.0","deprecated":false},{"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"name":"visionOS","introducedAt":"1.0","deprecated":false},{"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"name":"watchOS","introducedAt":"6.0","deprecated":false}],"extendedModule":"OpenSwiftUICore","title":"padding(_:_:)","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"padding","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4EdgeO","text":"Edge","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":".","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4EdgeO3SetV","text":"Set","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV","text":"CGFloat","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?) -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","text":"View","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"PaddingLayout.swift","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUICore\/Layout\/Modifier\/PaddingLayout.swift#L197"},"modules":[{"relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"],"name":"OpenSwiftUI"}],"externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewPAAE7paddingyQrAA4EdgeO3SetV_14CoreFoundation7CGFloatVSgtF::SYNTHESIZED::s:11OpenSwiftUI13EquatableViewV"},"references":{"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/EquatableView/padding(_:_:)":